@startuml
title Iterator - Estrutura

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class Client

interface Iterator {
  + hasNext(): boolean
  + next()
}

interface Aggregate {
  + createIterator(): Iterator
}

class ConcreteAggregate
class ConcreteIterator

Client --> Aggregate : solicita iterador
ConcreteAggregate ..|> Aggregate
ConcreteIterator ..|> Iterator
ConcreteAggregate --> ConcreteIterator : cria
Client --> Iterator : percorre

note right of ConcreteIterator
  Mantem o estado do percurso
  sem expor a estrutura interna
  da colecao ao cliente.
end note

@enduml

@startuml
title Iterator - Comunicação

actor Client
participant Aggregate
participant Iterator

Client -> Aggregate : createIterator()
Aggregate --> Client : iterator
loop enquanto houver elementos
  Client -> Iterator : hasNext()
  Iterator --> Client : true
  Client -> Iterator : next()
  Iterator --> Client : elemento atual
end

@enduml
